  29 Feb 2008; Carsten Lohrke <carlo@gentoo.org> ponyprog-2.07a.ebuild:
  Remove icon extension from desktop entry to match Icon Theme Specification.

  27 Aug 2007; Christoph Mende <angelos@gentoo.org> ponyprog-2.07a.ebuild:
  Added ~amd64 wrt bug #187146

  22 Jul 2007; Denis Dupeyron <calchan@gentoo.org> ponyprog-2.06c.ebuild:
  Removed virtual/x11 (obsolete) and sys-libs/glibc (implicit) dependencies.

